OL,3,CTrial witness in wrongful rape
OL,4,Cconviction 'had no doubt' over ID -
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FA witness in a trial told a jury he
OL,8,Fhad "no doubt" about the man he had
OL,9,Fpicked out in an identity parade, who
OL,10,Fwent on to serve 17 years in jail
OL,11,Fafter being wrongfully convicted of
OL,12,Frape.
OL,14,FMichael Seward, now deceased, had
OL,15,Fgiven evidence in the trial of Andrew
OL,16,FMalkinson, an innocent man accused of
OL,17,Fa brutal rape in Little Hulton,
OL,18,FSalford, in 2003.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@NO]
