PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773241885
OL,3,CTrial witness in wrongful rape
OL,4,Cconviction 'had no doubt' over ID -
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FThe rape victim, as well as Mr Seward
OL,8,Fand his then partner, Beverley Craig,
OL,9,Fall picked out Mr Malkinson as the
OL,10,Fattacker ` but he was in fact the
OL,11,Fvictim of a miscarriage of justice,
OL,12,FManchester Crown Court has heard.
OL,14,FMr Seward's evidence at the 2004 trial
OL,15,Fof Mr Malkinson was read on Tuesday to
OL,16,Fthe jury at the trial of Paul Quinn,
OL,17,F51, who was later linked to the rape
OL,18,Fby fresh DNA evidence after Mr
OL,19,FMalkinson was exonerated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
