PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773241885
OL,3,CTrial witness in wrongful rape
OL,4,Cconviction 'had no doubt' over ID -
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FMr Malkinson first appealed against
OL,8,Fhis conviction in 2006, but this was
OL,9,Fdismissed.
OL,11,FHe then made two more attempts, in
OL,12,F2009 and 2018, to ask the Criminal
OL,13,FCases Review Commission to send his
OL,14,Fcase to the Court of Appeal, but both
OL,15,Fwere rejected.
OL,17,FHis final attempt in 2021 led to his
OL,18,Fappeal against his conviction being
OL,19,Fallowed by the Court of Appeal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
