PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773241885
OL,3,CTrial witness in wrongful rape
OL,4,Cconviction 'had no doubt' over ID -
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FQuinn, aged 29 at the time of the
OL,8,Fattack and who lived locally before
OL,9,Fmoving to Exeter, Devon, was only
OL,10,Flinked to the crime years later, after
OL,11,Fscientific advances matched his DNA
OL,12,Fprofile from samples left on the
OL,13,Fvictim.
OL,15,FThe DNA findings estimate it would be
OL,16,Fat least one billion times more likely
OL,17,Fif Quinn was a contributor to the
OL,18,Fsample found at the crime scene than
OL,19,Fif he was not.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
