PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773241885
OL,3,CTrial witness in wrongful rape
OL,4,Cconviction 'had no doubt' over ID -
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FThe defendant has pleaded not guilty
OL,8,Fto two counts of rape, grievous bodily
OL,9,Fharm and attempting to choke or
OL,10,Fstrangle his victim to render her
OL,11,Funconscious while he carried out the
OL,12,Fattack.
OL,14,FThe trial was adjourned until
OL,15,FWednesday morning.
OL,17,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,18,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,19,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,20,Four region.
